@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
skinparam classBorderColor #6A1B9A
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Pending : process
Approved : entry / log comment
Pending --> Archived : review
Archived --> Reviewed : process
Archived : entry / log comment
Reviewed --> OnHold : approve
OnHold --> Approved : revert
OnHold --> [*]
@enduml